{"id": 1249, "genre": 1000, "title": "这年头，你有了哪些看电视剧的新习惯？", "description": "总之不会在电视机上看了。（题图来自：Eric Nyffeler）", "record_count": 16035, "comment_count": 45, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160930161041NiOfKkVspdZuYcmC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-05T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 1140, "title": "这年头，你有了哪些看电视剧的新习惯？", "content": "这年头，你有了哪些看电视剧的新习惯？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 120878, "content": "不爱追剧，会攒很多集一次看完", "image": "img/option/option/2016093016173028lN6YKiMxGVdLwb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120879, "content": "先下载/缓存好，在上下班路上看", "image": "img/option/option/2016093016221864CQFWEzjqRpHwt3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120883, "content": "把豆瓣和微信公众号的剧评都看一遍再决定要不要开始看一部剧", "image": "img/option/option/20160930162953PsYSxmwE5UXTB16C.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120884, "content": "周围朋友都在看什么就跟着看一看", "image": "img/option/option/20160930163228CJjP4DLnlE3uXKNp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120885, "content": "一边吃饭一边看剧", "image": "img/option/option/20160930163510UrfQnjJ8lFORbmi0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120887, "content": "把雷剧当综艺看，以吐槽为乐", "image": "img/option/option/20160930163714nEleJP3THwhZ9jmX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120888, "content": "一定要开弹幕", "image": "img/option/option/20160930163816nc51YBqDHWE86frx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120891, "content": "就算是在弹幕网站上看，也会关掉弹幕", "image": "img/option/option/20160930164317gqPRjueWHESIwUrJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 120895, "content": "找到一次能把所有剧集看完视频网站才会开始看", "image": "img/option/option/20160930165448tAfzqXMD50EUG3uQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}